---
import ImageLightbox from './ImageLightbox.astro';
---

<section class="projects" id="projects">
  <h2>My <span class="enfasis-title">Projects</span></h2>
  <div class="projects-grid">
    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img
          src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/gasoline-system.png`}
          alt="Fleet & Driver Management Microservices Platform"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>Fleet & Driver Management Platform</h3>

        <p>
          Distributed <strong>microservices-based platform</strong> for managing drivers, license types,
          vehicles (light/heavy), routes, and operational performance. Built with <strong
            >NestJS microservices</strong
          > integrated via <strong>Eureka Service Discovery</strong> and <strong>gRPC</strong>,
          exposing a unified API Gateway. Supports real-time route tracking using GPS-based APIs,
          performance indicators, fuel consumption metrics, and <strong
            >PDF report generation</strong
          >. Implements asynchronous messaging with <strong>RabbitMQ</strong>, optimized queries in <strong
            >PostgreSQL</strong
          >, and a <strong>React dashboard</strong> for system administration and analytics.
        </p>

        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-nestjs-plain colored"></i> NestJS</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-nodejs-plain colored"></i> Node.js</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-rabbitmq-original colored"></i> RabbitMQ</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-docker-plain colored"></i> Docker</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-grpc-plain colored"></i> gRPC</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-linux-plain colored"></i> Linux</span>
        </div>

        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/DavidJosueP2/Distributed-Gasoline-System" target="_blank">
            <i class="fab fa-github"></i> Backend Repo
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/JoelBonillaG/Distributed-Gasoline-System-Frontend"
            target="_blank"
          >
            <i class="fab fa-github"></i> Frontend Repo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img
          src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/amazon.png`}
          alt="E-Commerce Marketplace Platform"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>E-Commerce Marketplace Platform</h3>
        <p>
          Complete marketplace serving <strong>5,000+ users</strong> with Spring Boot backend and React/TypeScript
          frontend. Features RESTful APIs with JWT/RBAC security, pagination, and content moderation.
          Achieved <strong>85% response time improvement</strong> (300ms → 45ms) through Redis multi-layer
          caching and database optimization. Deployed with CI/CD using Jenkins, SonarQube, and Azure Container
          Apps with <strong>90% test coverage</strong> and 95+ Lighthouse score.
        </p>
        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-spring-original colored"></i> Spring Boot</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-redis-plain colored"></i> Redis</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-typescript-plain colored"></i> TypeScript</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-tailwindcss-original colored"></i> TailwindCSS</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-jenkins-plain colored"></i> Jenkins</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-azure-plain colored"></i> Azure</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <!-- <a href="https://drtx2.github.io/copying-amazon/#/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> Live Demo</a> -->
          <a href="https://github.com/DavidJosueP2/Marketplace_Link" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Backend Source Code</a
          >
          <a href="https://github.com/DavidJosueP2/Marketplace-Link-Front" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Frontend Source Code</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img
          src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/clinic-front.jpeg`}
          alt="Medical Clinic Management System"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>Medical Clinic Management System</h3>
        <p>
          HIPAA-compliant full-stack healthcare system with a <strong
            >Clean Architecture backend</strong
          > managing appointments, medical history, and audit trails. Includes <strong
            >React admin dashboard</strong
          > for system administrators and <strong
            >React dashboard for healthcare professionals</strong
          > to manage their patients and schedules. Features <strong>React Native mobile app</strong
          > for patients to view medical history, receive notifications, discover doctors, and manage
          their profile. Optimized data retrieval with <strong
            >3NF normalization and indexing</strong
          >, achieving <strong>60% faster access to medical records</strong>, plus <strong
            >rate limiting</strong
          > and <strong>cache invalidation</strong> for reliability.
        </p>

        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-spring-original colored"></i> Spring Boot</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-redis-plain colored"></i> Redis</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React Native</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-tailwindcss-original colored"></i> TailwindCSS</span>
          <span
            ><i
              ><img
                src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/icons8-json-web-token.svg`}
                alt=""
              /></i
            > JWT/RBAC</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/clinic" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img
          src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/maintenance_system.png`}
          alt="Inventory Management and Judicial Audits System"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>Inventory Management and Judicial Audits System</h3>
        <p>
          Web system for state entities that manages inventories, users with custom roles, and
          mandatory maintenance compliance per Ecuadorian law. Tracks asset maintenance schedules,
          generates dynamic PDF reports for judicial audits, and ensures security with JWT
          authentication. Features performance and compliance reporting aligned with public sector
          regulations.
        </p>
        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-laravel-original colored"></i> Laravel</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-mysql-original colored"></i> MySQL</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-materialui-plain colored"></i> Material UI</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-figma-plain colored"></i> Figma</span>
          <span
            ><i
              ><img
                src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/icons8-json-web-token.svg`}
                alt=""
              /></i
            > JWT</span
          >
          <span><i class="devicon-axios-plain colored"></i> Axios</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/maintenance-system" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img
          src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/smartnotes.png`}
          alt="SmartNotes Microservices Platform"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>SmartNotes Platform — Microservices Architecture</h3>
        <p>
          Scalable note-taking platform built with microservices architecture using NestJS and
          TypeScript. Implements event-driven communication with RabbitMQ, NGINX as API Gateway for
          routing and authentication, and secure MongoDB/PostgreSQL schemas with proper indexing.
          Features JWT + RBAC authentication, containerized services with Docker, and comprehensive
          testing with Jest.
        </p>
        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-nestjs-original colored"></i> NestJS</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-typescript-plain colored"></i> TypeScript</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-rabbitmq-original colored"></i> RabbitMQ</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-mongodb-original colored"></i> MongoDB</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-nginx-original colored"></i> NGINX</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-docker-plain colored"></i> Docker</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/note-app" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/uta_page.jpeg`} alt="UTA Elections Page" />
      </div>
      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>UTA Elections Page</h3>
        <p>
          A digital platform supporting Dr. Mary Cruz Lascano's 2024-2028 rectorial campaign at the
          Technical University of Ambato. It informs and connects stakeholders with campaign
          details, proposals, events, news, and real-time statistics. Built with Laravel, Bootstrap,
          and MySQL, it ensures functionality and modern design.
        </p>
        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-laravel-original colored"></i> Laravel</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-javascript-plain colored"></i> JavaScript</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain colored"></i> Bootstrap</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-mysql-original colored"></i> MySQL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://gitlab.com/personalprojects5531442/manejo-proyecto/" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/blog.jpeg`} alt="My Creative Portfolio" />
      </div>
      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>My Creative Portfolio</h3>
        <p>
          My Creative Portfolio is an interactive platform for creating and customizing personal
          portfolios. It allows users to showcase work professionally, manage projects, and engage
          with a creative community through comments and collaboration.
        </p>
        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-php-plain colored"></i> PHP</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-javascript-plain colored"></i> JavaScript</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-axios-plain colored"></i> Axios</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-mysql-original colored"></i> MySQL</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain colored"></i> Bootstrap</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/proyecto-mds.git" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project">
      <div class="project-image">
        <img
          src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/img/capibara.jpeg`}
          alt="Clean Architecture Adventure Game"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="project-content">
        <h3>Clean Architecture Adventure</h3>
        <p>
          A <strong>Unity 2D adventure game</strong> built as a <strong>technical showcase</strong> of
          <strong>Clean Architecture</strong> and <strong>SOLID principles</strong>. Players
          traverse
          <strong>parkour-style levels</strong> and engage in combat against diverse enemies, while the
          system manages <strong>user authentication</strong>, <strong>level progression</strong>,
          and
          <strong>SQLite-based persistence</strong> for game state and player data. The project features
          a
          <strong>highly decoupled and scalable codebase</strong> implementing design patterns such as
          <strong>Singleton, Observer, Factory, Abstract Factory, Strategy, and Event Bus</strong>,
          demonstrating how <strong>enterprise-grade software architecture</strong> can be effectively
          applied to game development.
        </p>

        <div class="technologies">
          <span><i class="devicon-csharp-plain colored"></i> C#</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-unity-plain colored"></i> Unity</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-sqlite-plain colored"></i> SQLite</span>
          <span><i class="devicon-dotnetcore-plain colored"></i> .NET</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/PatternsProject/tree/develop" target="_blank"
            ><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

